content:
The new Rules allow me to do some of the things for which I have been using Tasker, BUT

1. I cannot see how to have Do Not Disturb turn of when I disconnect from the specified WiFi or leave the specified location;

2. The WiFi Rule is in fact not quite as convenient as Tasker's because Tasker allows "WiFi Near" as a trigger and does not require connection to the specified WiFi.
